Title: Cross-Jurisdictions
Plot: Grissom and his crew handle their highest profile case to date when the city's former chief of detectives is slain execution-style in his house following a wild party. Missing from the residence are the chief's trophy wife and their 7-year-old daughter.  Catherine and Warrick follow the trail to Miami, and soon enlist the help of Horatio Caine.
Writer: Anthony E. Zuiker, Ann Donahue, Carol Mendelsohn
